data.title: Sandhills Magazine
data.meta_description: Sandhills Magazine provides news and information about Sandhills Publishings unique publications and information processing services in the construction, trucking, aircraft, agriculture, and computer industries. Stay up to date on the latest in company news and the many services Sandhills Publishing offers including hosted email service, customer relations management via Microsoft CRM, custom hosted websites, and more.
